The '''Fernandin Scouting Expedition''' was an exploratory body that inhabited the [[Great Temple/Legends|Great Massassi Temple]] on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]] after the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] evacuated the base several months after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. The expedition remained there until after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], when they ran out of funding.

